com.swirl

Class VisitManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.swirl.Manager
      • com.swirl.VisitManager

  • public class VisitManager
extends Manager
    The VisitManager consumes the various Enter/Exit/Dwell events from the BeaconManager, the WifiManager, and the RegionManager and tracks enter and exit times, accumulates dwell and elapsed times by location and placement, and generates logical Visit objects and posts Visit events onto the EventBus.

    An instance of this class is loaded and started by the library. You do not interact with this class directly.

      • getActiveLocationVisits

        public java.util.ArrayList<Visit> getActiveLocationVisits()
        Get a list of the active (ongoing) Location Visits sorted by quality and distance (nearest and highest quality to farthest and lowest quality). This list is for the Location only Visits.

        Visits are sorted by type Beacon, Wifi, Region and by distance from device within each type.
        Returns:
        sorted list of Visits.

      • getActivePlacementVisits

        Returns:
